description: Capacity Building, Cooperation and Victims Assis. for National and Local Mechanisms to Combat Trafficking of Armenians

subproject.corporate outcome: Strengthened capacities of national human rights institutions
subproject.description:
CP 2005-2009: National legislative and policy frameworks and institutional capacity on trafficking in persons are strengthened; anti-trafficking efforts are harmonized regionally.

CP 2010-2015, OUTPUT 2.1.4: Capacity of government institutions to manage borders, migration, combat trafficking and effectively protect their rights enhanced.

Project title: Anti-Trafficking Programme: Capacity Developing Support: Phase II
